		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You spin a tiny prismatic diamond in your hand, catching the light and refracting its many colors to generate a flying sphere of energy.</em></p><p><strong>Materials</strong>: You require a @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.FePPX5VU9YzmXpdU]{Tiny Prismatic Diamond}, typically valued at 50 gold.</p><p><strong>Ranged Spell Attack</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Target takes [[/damage]] damage.* You choose the damage type.</p></li><li><p>If two or more of the damage d8s show the same number, the orb leaps to another creature of your choice within 30 ft. of the target. Make a new attack and damage roll for that creature. A creature can be targeted only once by each casting.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d8 type=acid/cold/lightning/fire/poison/thunder]] for each spell slot level above 1st. <br /></p>",
